name: Vibrato Coral
details:
Vibrato - Chorus - DelayThe Vibrato Coral is a new multipurpose modulation delay device.
It has many controls: delay time, delay feedback, modulation depth, modulation rate, wet signal volume, modulation shape (square or triangle), mode (wet + dry or just wet).
By being able to control so many parameters you can make the Vibrato Coral work as:
Vibrato
Chorus
Modulated delay
Weird pitch shifter
and more...
This pedal has enough low end to handle guitar and bass just as well!
Made in Costa Rica!
Knobs size and colors may change.
Typical enclosure size: 3.82" x 1.50" x 1.22"
All pedals come with hand stamped labels and bare metal enclosures.
True bypass. 9V center negative standard 2.1mm Boss Style dc jack (adapter not included).
